  m_text: "<align=center><size=55><b>Privacy Policy</b></size></align>\n\nContact
    Email: ziiohuio22@outlook.com\nEffective Date: March 2026\nDesire Girls: Mahjong
    Match (\"we\", \"our\", or \"us\") is committed to protecting your privacy. This
    Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when
    you use our mobile application.\n\nBy using the app, you agree to the collection
    and use of information in accordance with this policy.\n\n<size=40><b>1. Information
    We Collect</b></size>\nWe may collect certain information automatically when
    you use our app, including:\n\u2022 Device type and operating system\n\u2022
    App usage data and gameplay progress\n\u2022 IP address and general location
    information\n\u2022 Advertising identifiers (such as Google Advertising ID)\n\nThis
    information is collected to improve app performance and user experience.\n\n<size=40><b>2.
    In-App Purchases</b></size>\nOur app may offer in-app purchases. Purchases are
    processed securely through Google Play.\nWe do not collect or store your payment
    information. All payment-related information is handled by Google Play according
    to their privacy policy.\n\n<size=40><b>3. Advertising</b></size>\nWe may use
    third-party advertising services that may collect and use information to provide
    personalized ads.\nThese third-party services may include but are not limited
    to:\n\u2022 Google AdMob\n\u2022 Unity Ads\n\u2022 AppLovin\n\u2022 Other advertising
    partners\n\nThese services may collect device identifiers and usage data to deliver
    relevant advertisements.\n\n<size=40><b>4. How We Use Information</b></size>\nWe
    may use the collected information to:\n\u2022 Improve gameplay experience\n\u2022
    Maintain app performance\n\u2022 Provide customer support\n\u2022 Deliver relevant
    advertisements\n\u2022 Analyze usage trends\n\n<size=40><b>5. Data Security</b></size>\nWe
    take reasonable measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission
    over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.\n\n<size=40><b>6. Children's
    Privacy</b></size>\nThis service is not directed to children under the age of
    13. The game does not knowingly collect personal information from children under
    13 years of age.\nIf a user is under 13 years old, they may only use and access
    the game with the involvement of a parent or guardian. If parents believe that
    their child has submitted personal information to the game, they may contact
    us via the email listed below.\nIf we become aware that a child under 13 has
    provided us with personal information, we will promptly delete such information
    from our records. We recognize the importance of protecting children's privacy
    and encourage parents to regularly monitor their children's online activities.\n\n<size=40><b>7.
    Third-Party Services</b></size>\nThe app may use third-party services that may
    collect information used to identify you.\nWe encourage you to review their privacy
    policies.\n\n<size=40><b>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</b></size>\nWe may
    update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this
    page\n\n<size=40><b>9. Contact Us</b></size>\nIf you have any questions about
    this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at:\nEmail: <u>ziiohuio22@outlook.com\n</u>"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: bab5ef41f3528044fb14315a452db98d, type: 2}
